      <description><![CDATA[KISSIMMEE, FLORIDA  A Florida family isn't quite laughing after a Snapchat video of their little girl freaking out at some guy in an Easter Bunny outfit went viral. It's safe to say the 2-year-old was a little shocked when the Easter Bunny came into class to say hi the other day.  The family told ABC News that they didn't find out until after the video went viral, unfortunately they don't find it quite as amusing. The family also said people's comments have been rather unpleasant. Well, welcome to the internet. But hey, at least now she's an Easter legend.]]></description>
